Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我說 你跟魯魯修發展的怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是學校公認的一對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經接過吻了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那只不過是活動而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還什麼都沒做呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著害羞 大家都知道你喜歡魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.90,0:00:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 連維蕾塔老師也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是喜歡他嗎 喜歡到為了包庇他而向我開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都得堆滿笑容與向自己開槍的女人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不得不戴著身為教師的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉·費列特 你真有膽量敢向我開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 魯魯是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害死父親的仇人


Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自過去的刺客


Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍門關已經陷落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澳門的空軍設施也已經鎮壓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈薩克斯坦的守衛任務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把朝比奈和洪古調過去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建業的內政就交由水無瀨和杉山負責嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來進行得很順利呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是敵軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不過是那些不肯接受我們的地方軍閥 在各地舉兵而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠統一地方軍閥的帥印 已經被哥哥率先得到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看池袋的情況 等我回來再繼續幫你的功課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.86,0:04:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維蕾塔老師是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮是黑騎士團的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妮娜呢?會長呢?利瓦爾呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的就只有學校嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼娜娜會成總督?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼是真什麼是假
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}普通快車將遲到10分鐘到達3號站台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}最先前往大久保方向的普通列車將從2號站台發車…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 作為初期準備已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就按這個樣式繼續作業
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}現在向各位顧客發佈優惠活動的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}現在 期間限定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 突然叫我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修呢 在約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去做G列車的測試去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 你為什麼倒戈了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我不同 既然是教團派來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哥哥和我之間…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B7報告司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮拜堂附近發現可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B5和B9已經前去確認了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是問魯魯修在哪裡就有如此行動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞卿…為什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對象正在前往俱樂部會所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B2 B8被除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播報校內廣播 讓別的學生遠離對象區域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在向各位在校同學發佈緊急通知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要靠近俱樂部會所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有報告說看到可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到萬不得已 我不想殺女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也儘量想避免無謂的殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都多虧了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說要弑神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜大概是某種比喻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少他們是這樣堅信著的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.82,0:06:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢 神明什麼的根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有什麼背後長著翅膀的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是長鬍子老人這樣的神存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科奈莉婭殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道他會用什麼GEASS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說對手是小孩 也不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不愧是大名鼎鼎的科奈莉婭皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.24,0:07:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為你的伯父 我也為你感到驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾立誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.13,0:07:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「既然存在著讓人互相爭鬥的神明 還是乾脆殺掉的好」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是改造人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要破壞了裸露的身體部分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手方位沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會阻止你!為了魯魯修大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不錯的攻防體術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對我 傑雷米亞·哥德巴爾德卻是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲世子!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剝奪你的時間!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲世子 趁我把這傢伙定住的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…我的GEASS被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對停止的結界被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛·蘭佩洛奇 果然已經被籠絡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼GEASS會…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為這樣我才會作為教團的刺客被選上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是來殺哥哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞卿!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維蕾塔!?你也被魯魯修籠絡了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修現在正在池袋的車站大樓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 傑雷米亞卿 快把我解放出來吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然把朱雀君叫了出來 但該說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 魯魯也在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉 你想做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是朱雀約她出來的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利瓦爾說魯魯修一直待在日本的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機情局的報告也證明他是清白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 為什麼我還是不相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維蕾塔 你打算背叛哥哥嗎? 還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟魯魯修取得聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡我守著就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟魯魯修會合的話應該能夾擊傑雷米亞卿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得跟朱雀君說才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯是ZERO 是害死父親的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是分界線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租界和貧民區
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是總有一天我要讓分界線消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 如果他們倆是共犯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓11區變回日本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 兩人以前就是好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了? 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子 明明大家都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放開我 放開我!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行! 我不放!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…我已經不想再失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都…不想再失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 以前也發生過相同的事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你們想抓住亞瑟的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實發生過那種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次拉你起來的都是朱雀君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修在上面的話 兩個人早就掉下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個體力白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要這麼說的話 在掉下去之前就可以救我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在笑什麼 魯魯修是把尤菲給…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 魯魯 是一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:11:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 要當心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞往你那裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是教團的刺客 我的GEASS對他無效
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙還活著?刺客是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 總之我到達之前不要亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 朱雀在的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不像是朋友打來的電話啊 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的哦 朱雀君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是應該先辦我的事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 你們倆約好見面的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等等嗎? 我先…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧朱雀君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡將會成為戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為夏莉的安全著想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朱雀在一起應該是最佳選擇…


Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傑雷米亞·哥德巴爾德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有防彈措施
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.21,0:13:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中了魯魯修的GEASS嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止GEASS對他無效
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有解除的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著火了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恐怖襲擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 有本事就上來吧 Orange
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的要事是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我喜歡魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀討厭他嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…曾喜歡過…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.04,0:14:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明你們倆以前感情這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能原諒他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼事是不能原諒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是朱雀沒有原諒他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想原諒他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就已經原諒他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要聯絡消防局嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不應該是先向軍方優先報告的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀況…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Knight of Seven 樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…真是冒犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有可能是恐怖襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在由我來指揮周圍的警備和消防事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想請你保護她的人身安全
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 現在還是會議中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒叫上我的會議 誰去管它這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自ZERO的緊急聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得很微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 我是扇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急事件是?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果擔心台灣人的話 現在正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完成了平民的疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進到車裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.17,0:15:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Knight of Seven大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你孤身一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你從我手心上逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯到底在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯 一個人在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械身體 外加GEASS Canceller
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的執著可不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Orange君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是執著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是忠義
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是聽不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那狗皇帝有何為他鞠躬盡瘁的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這性能 果然用了Sakuradite啊

Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gefion Disturber

Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你功課做得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你應該很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這干擾Sakuradite的系統完成的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能使環狀線內的都市機能完全癱瘓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 能使東京靜止下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.67,0:17:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了 你是個很好的實驗品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡魯魯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教團的位置 以及V.V.身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該全盤托出的 是你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有 理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡忠到底的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要確認事情的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 不可能還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修啊 你為何要披上ZERO的外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與祖國布里塔尼亞以及親生父親為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為我是魯魯修·V·布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的生父布里塔尼亞皇帝對母親見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此還導致娜娜莉雙目失明雙腿癱瘓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.69,0:18:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還奪去了我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也在事發現場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的首次任務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為敬愛的瑪麗安娜皇妃的護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻沒能保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能盡忠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才成立了純血派的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成為ZERO 果然是為了瑪麗安娜大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是來殺我的 而是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主君不是V.V.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是 瑪麗安娜大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來 我就毫無牽掛了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞卿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞·哥德巴爾德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒完成盡忠的使命呢 沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Your Majesty
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡啊 畢竟是我唯一的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你是魯魯同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 讓我也加入你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想守護魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想幫魯魯奪回屬於他的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連妹妹娜娜也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我讓傑雷米亞先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會為我清除障礙的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別和他發生衝突 已經是同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰做出這種事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後能和你說上話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是最後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就找醫生 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恢復記憶時 感覺很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛假的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去記憶的朋友們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺全世界都在監視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯是單身在這樣的世界作戰的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想 只有我才能給魯魯一個真實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.10,0:20:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管知道 爸爸也是被你牽扯進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你卻怎麼也恨不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.66,0:20:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然魯魯讓我忘記了發生的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我又喜歡上了魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管記憶被人篡改
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又喜歡上了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別死 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管轉世投胎幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定還是會喜歡上魯魯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是命運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別死 夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別死 別死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…可以的吧 魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是轉世投胎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能喜歡上你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上你…很多次…很多次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏莉 夏莉

Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.99,0:23:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,過去C.C.曾對我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Geass是王的力量 會讓你變得孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.97,0:23:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,夏莉 我一直很想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.11,0:23:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你被我的Geass捲入混亂 最後成為了犧牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:23:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底該如何贖罪才可以
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我 告訴我吧…
